					<msContents class="#CM">
						<summary><p>Transcriptions of Tamil inscriptions by Ariel, bound in one volume. Various papers of various format, pasted (f2-f8) or bound in the volume (f9-f27). Contains also drawings. </p>
<p>The volume contains:
  <list rend="numbered">
    <item><locus facs="0">f1-f1<hi rend="superscript">2</hi></locus>: title page and drawings.</item>
    <item><locus facs="0">f2-f7</locus>: transcription of an inscription in Tamil script.</item>
    <item><locus facs="0">f8-f18</locus>: drawings with inscriptions transcribed in Tamil at their location on the wall and base.</item>
    <item><locus facs="0">f19-f20</locus>: drawings.</item>
        <item><locus facs="0">f21-f26</locus>: drawings with inscriptions transcribed in Tamil at their location on the wall and base.</item>
    <item><locus facs="0">f27</locus>: drawings (recto) and notes (verso).</item>
    
      </list>
</p></summary>

						
